# Rendered demo media is regenerable from assets/*.tape (`vhs assets/demo.tape`)
# and hosted on GitHub's asset CDN, never committed — a binary blob is permanent
# in git history. "Derive, don't store": the .tape is the source, the GIF is output.
assets/*.gif
assets/*.mp4

# Full verbatim PokeAPI responses — politeness cache only. Committed, filtered
# versions of just the fields our DTOs read live under data/raw/pokeapi/.
